Content:
@jl777c your contribution to the community with your development work, along with your public relations and openness to discuss all things Komodo with everyone and anyone has been of huge benefit to the community and project. You're an extremely open and honest person to talk to. You take no shit and say it how it is, whilst taking into account other peoples point of view. I dont know any other project that has any developers that do that. You should take pride in that and people should appreciate that. 
Specifically, I'd like to thank you for all the work you do. 
I'd also like to remind everyone about tbe experience they're having with you, and how valuable that is. What other discord would you be having 1 on 1 conversations with such a talented developer of such a professional organisation.
